{"questionId":"33299990","questionHtml":"<p>Write down the equation for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi></math> in the form <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>f</mi><mfenced><mi>x</mi></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;(accept <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math>, accept&nbsp; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>m</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp; and&nbsp; <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>c</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for correct gradient, <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for correct <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>y</mi></math>-intercept</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"33299990","referenceCode":"24N.1.SL.TZ1.7a","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Write down the equation for f in the form fx=mx+c.","paper":"1","level":"SL","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.1—Equations of straight lines, parallel and perpendicular"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}